{"tid":1220450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[持久遊擊戰術] 想分享一個羅馬既歷史故事","createTime":"2019-06-14T04:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:36:29.000Z","uid":27963,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6adf95dc3c3d364365fae11524fe2ce19b1c6d07","tid":1220450,"uid":27963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"暫時星期一前立法會都唔會開會，抗爭已經演變成持久戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而立法會喺7月10日後就會放暑假兩個半月<br />\n假設政府堅持唔撤回逃犯條例一定要開會二讀<br />\n我地既目標期限最遲就係拖到7月10日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺決定呢個持久戰既大戰略時，我地最需要既係組織力<br />\n呢個時候我諗起一個歷史故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺公元前218年，迦太基名將漢尼拔奇蹟地翻越阿爾卑斯山<br />\n對羅馬發起長達16年既「第二次布匿戰爭」<br />\n仲即刻連贏兩場大戰役，令羅馬城面臨被圍城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候，費邊臨危受命做獨裁官指揮軍隊守衛國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n漢尼拔無即刻攻羅馬城，而喺意大利周圍破壞洗劫，瓦解羅馬既統治<br />\n面對漢尼拔既逆襲，羅馬人多但戰鬥力差好遠，究竟點算好呢？<br />\n費邊諗到一套戰術，一套好小學雞既「跟尾狗」戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n漢尼拔打到邊，佢就跟到邊，一直牽制而不戰<br />\n漢尼拔果陣既諗法應該會係咁：<br />\n「好似有一隻烏蠅摟住，嗡嗡&hellip;對唔住，唔係一隻，係一堆烏蠅喺你耳仔邊，一路飛入你嘅腦裏邊，救命啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n雖然費邊戰術算成功，但不得民心羅馬人想速戰速決趕走漢尼拔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n避免羅馬既城市再受漢尼拔既虐待<br />\n於是佢地笑鳩費邊，幫佢起左個朵叫「拖延者」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好快一年期滿後就比人撤換下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢落台後，羅馬人即刻吹大雞同漢尼拔打左場「坎尼決戰」<br />\n然後即刻就死左全國20%人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n漢尼拔繼續周圍打，好快好多城市都戰敗/投降<br />\n羅馬民族到左最危險既時候<br />\n每個人都被逼發出最後既吼聲<br />\n<br />\n「費邊，費邊，費邊！」<br />\n事隔一年，拖延者費邊當選執政官上台救亡<br />\n繼續實行佢既費邊戰術拖延時間，唔同既係佢今次都有打遊擊<br />\n「敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我進」<br />\n佢主力打番失去既羅馬城市，同時焦土斷絕迦太基既補給線<br />\n但又避免同漢尼拔硬碰硬<br />\n羅馬有以逸待勞優勢，同漢尼拔陷入膠著<br />\n最後先慢慢反CUP<br />\n喺16年後成功打贏「第二次布匿戰爭」<br />\n<br />\n而家我地既情況同羅馬一樣，贏人數但輸戰鬥力<br />\n過於勇武硬碰硬好輸蝕<br />\n急進行事又會令我地體力不繼失去組織力<br />\n但我地既勝利條件同羅馬一樣：<br />\n拖延時間拖到佢地急，拖到最遲7月10日<br />\n喺呢個情況下遊擊戰似乎係最好既選項<br />\n至於點遊擊法，就靠大家既想像啦<br />\n可以係示威、可以係金融/貨幣、可以係交通層面<br />\n歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94e89b84249ed1269a6455aa3c3d9b993b901a7","tid":1220450,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed25f867611e3bd014be3914a176b6e9028e051d","tid":1220450,"uid":7718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:17:06.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"d7328c906cd4a824332b2d7ec5e06b28f87f1ac1","tid":1220450,"uid":27963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n希望大家都知道呢一套費邊戰術<br />\n無論係金鐘，定係十八區，都拉長戰線令政府疲於奔命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb2cfad1a74057e8a387e9109762ec60e4bd680","tid":1220450,"uid":179283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"每個星期日遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40d563c2cec44b3c1620563c0bc0949d5b3a53b","tid":1220450,"uid":27963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb2cfad1a74057e8a387e9109762ec60e4bd680","tid":1220450,"uid":179283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"每個星期日遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"呢樣野我反而建議今星期試左先睇下點<br />\n一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭<br />\n其實今星期日遊行既聲勢反而係有少少「衰」左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91027740e8243472f7828d60413f4dce7613c888","tid":1220450,"uid":27963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"abd644ee8aa0cc2a126a426713bf95cb52d282f5","tid":1220450,"uid":27963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"記住避免同警方正面衝突<br />\n千奇唔好主動郁手<br />\n我地係要拖延開會時間<br />\n你地有無見過人踢波想拖延時間仲會主動攻?"},{"pid":"03a4f43412a6bd687d769a6b0976ddf6d7921a9a","tid":1220450,"uid":118631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日記得去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b16a382782ba6f6dce7bc2e834405bcab0f9de","tid":1220450,"uid":27963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03a4f43412a6bd687d769a6b0976ddf6d7921a9a","tid":1220450,"uid":118631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日記得去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一步"},{"pid":"28b9f989e8346256e28e54a0efe6687cbca90403","tid":1220450,"uid":27963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b710fee2433fa1b641eb1bd495b67eeb7fb628","tid":1220450,"uid":7718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519ff69da31065a2e26d977a79220f6269001a6c","tid":1220450,"uid":50149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8833d295c6315ab30d76192ca8efa318ce7c7b8e","tid":1220450,"uid":190218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:27:00.000Z","msg":"拍大巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b692037606b5b8b663ff7b049f0d83bfac5312","tid":1220450,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:35:47.000Z","msg":"其實只要佢一開立法會<br />\n果日就集中圍佢中環<br />\n<br />\n只要佢一拖，就全港遍地開花，佢拖一日就蝕一日錢<br />\n咁佢最好收回，唔收回搵錢城市香港就唔搵錢<br />\n<br />\n尤其是交通，主要幹道炒車/死火唔行得你唔係告我呀？<br />\n交通一塞時間一浪費，一日唔見一百億濕濕碎<br />\n又唔會俾人炒 我被罷工冇計<br />\n<br />\n唔想罷果啲藍絲嘈? <br />\n扺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa17bd3ca8aa468e665c5404c93d37396deaa95","tid":1220450,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實只要佢一開立法會<br />\n果日就集中圍佢金鐘<br />\n<br />\n只要佢一拖，就全港遍地開花，佢拖一日就蝕一日錢<br />\n咁佢最好收回，唔收回搵錢城市香港就唔搵錢<br />\n<br />\n尤其是交通，主要幹道炒車/死火唔行得你唔係告我呀？<br />\n交通一塞時間一浪費，一日唔見一百億濕濕碎<br />\n又唔會俾人炒 我被罷工冇計<br />\n<br />\n唔想罷果啲藍絲嘈? <br />\n扺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6a694bdf5c43ea3a4ba59f897140e396b92c4e5a","tid":1220450,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"多管齊下，各路人馬一齊團結合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}